00179  * @def DBUS_EXPORT
00180  *
00181  * Declare the following symbol as public.  This is currently a noop on
00182  * platforms other than Windows.
00183  */

00185 #if defined(DBUS_EXPORT)
00186   /* value forced by compiler command line, don't redefine */
00187 #elif defined(_WIN32)
00188 #  if defined(DBUS_STATIC_BUILD)
00189 #  define DBUS_EXPORT
00190 #  elif defined(dbus_1_EXPORTS)
00191 #  define DBUS_EXPORT __declspec(dllexport)
00192 #  else
00193 #  define DBUS_EXPORT __declspec(dllimport)
00194 #  endif
00195 #elif defined(__GNUC__) && __GNUC__ >= 4
00196 #  define DBUS_EXPORT __attribute__ ((__visibility__ ("default")))
00197 #else
00198 #define DBUS_EXPORT
00199 #endif
00200 
00201 #if defined(DBUS_PRIVATE_EXPORT)
00202   /* value forced by compiler command line, don't redefine */
00203 #elif defined(_WIN32)
00204 #  if defined(DBUS_STATIC_BUILD)
00205 #    define DBUS_PRIVATE_EXPORT /* no decoration */
00206 #  elif defined(dbus_1_EXPORTS)
00207 #    define DBUS_PRIVATE_EXPORT __declspec(dllexport)
00208 #  else
00209 #    define DBUS_PRIVATE_EXPORT __declspec(dllimport)
00210 #  endif
00211 #elif defined(__GNUC__) && __GNUC__ >= 4
00212 #  define DBUS_PRIVATE_EXPORT __attribute__ ((__visibility__ ("default")))
